<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, December 14 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange on Monday closed at 1,555.85 points, up
0.13 points from Sunday's finish.
</P>
