<HEADLINE> Saudi FM, EU Envoy Discuss Mideast Peace </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, December 14 (Xinhua) -- Saudi Foreign Minister
Saud Al-Faisal held talks in Riyadh Monday with visiting European
Union (EU) envoy Miguel Moratinos on the latest developments in
the Middle East peace process in light of the Wye Plantation
agreement.
