<HEADLINE> Foreign Investment in Russia Sharply Declines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Foreign investment in Russia
totaled 1.5882 billion U.S. dollars in the third quarter of 1998,
down 57.4 percent from the previous quarter, the Interfax news
agency reported on Tuesday.
</P>
