issuance of Euro yen notes to be managed by Nomura International
and 10 percent would be notes without the benefit of MITI
insurance.
</P>
<P>
Mustapa said the loan was not part of the
30-billion-U.S.-dollar Miyazawa initiative announced by Tokyo
recently to help Asian economies affected by the economic crisis,
from which Malaysia is expected to get a portion. 
