rival's style, completing a 3-1 victory over the 1988 Olympic
champion who finished runner-up to Deng in the Atlanta Olympic
Games.
</P>
<P>
Wang Nan, known from her composure and consistent play, came
from one set down to crush the South Korean best player in four
sets.
</P>
