Palestinian self-rule areas as a reflection of the U.S. commitment
to backing the peace process until the just, lasting and
comprehensive peace is achieved in the region.
</P>
<P>
He emphasized that any peace arrangements should guarantee
Palestinian people's national rights, including their right to
"create their independent state on their national soil".
</P>
<P>
The minister also expressed hopes that Clinton's visit will
lead to the full implementation of the Wye agreement in line with
the timetable agreed upon between Palestinians and Israelis.
</P>
<P>
U.S. Secretary of State Madeleine Albright is expected to
arrive in Amman later Tuesday to brief Jordanian leaders on
Clinton's visit to the Middle East. 
