<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Li Xuemei and Koji Ito,
winners in the women's and men's 100 meters respectively, anchored
vicotries for their countries in the 4x100m relays here on Tuesday
at the Asian Games.
