China respects the social system and the development path
chosen by the Mongolian people in accordance with their national
conditions and hopes that Mongolia will enjoy political stability
and economic prosperity, Wei noted.
</P>
<P>
China is ready to work with Mongolia for the establishment of a
long-term, stable, healthy and good-neighborly bilateral
relationship oriented to the next century, Wei said.
</P>
<P>
