<HEADLINE> Kuala Lumpur Stocks Close Mixed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed mixed Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
At the close, the 100-quality stocks Composite Index rose 3.78
points to 543.79, the all-share Emas Index shed 0.21 of a point to
143.54, the Industrial Index gained 6.28 points to 1,029.51 and
