<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 15 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on
the Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,194.84 points today,
down 1.45 points from the previous session, according to the
Guangfa Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
