<HEADLINE> Chinese Wang Retains Asiad Women's Pursuit Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 15 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Wang Qingzhi
successfully defended her women's 3-km individual pursuit title at
the Asian Games here on Tuesday, beating compatriot Zhao Haijuan
to second.
</P>
<P>
