said she wanted to concentrate more on her provincial coaching job
and phased out from competition.
</P>
<P>
"I could also make room for the newcomers like Zhao," added the
national champion.
</P>
<P>
Zhao, who won the road time trial gold here, was taken over by
Wang after one kilometer to end the game.
</P>
