and crimes against humanity for his role in the 1994 massacre of
over 500,000 people.
</P>
<P>
The People
</P>
<P>
-- After winning a major vote of confidence from Uganda's
mainly Western donors, President Yoweri Museveni must now assault
the twin problems of military spending and corruption that
threaten future funding, diplomats said Monday. 
</P>
