<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, December 14 (Xinhua) -- Yugoslav border guards killed
30 ethnic Albanian fighters and injured 12 more who were trying to
enter Kosovo from Albania on Monday, said the Serbian information
center in Pristina, capital of Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
The ethnic Albanians, wearing uniforms of the outlawed Kosovo
Liberation Army (KLA), attempted to cross from neighboring Albania
into Kosovo before dawn.
</P>
